sentence: How many lecture sections are offered for EECS 482 next semester ?
sentence-with-vars: How many lecture sections are offered for department0 number0 next semester ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( * ) FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 482 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
